
'''* Book: Under, Against, Beyond: Labour and Social Movements Confront a Globalised, Informatised, Capitalism. By Waterman Peter'''

URL = http://www.into-ebooks.com/book/under-against-beyond/


=Description=

"Almost 1000 pages of Peter Waterman’s Working Papers on labour and global movements. Peter Waterman (London 1936) is a veteran activist-researcher in and on labour, social movements, the old and new internationalisms.

Waterman produced this set with the Institute of Social Studies, The Hague, between the 1980s and the 2000s. The Working Papers are presented in chronological order. Many of the final form versions have been shortened, they are scattered in books, magazines and journals worldwide. Some have never reached final-form publication."
(http://www.into-ebooks.com/book/under-against-beyond/)


